# Where should we write the GIF?
Output demo_tab_completion_easing.gif
Output demo_tab_completion_easing.svg

Source demo_settings.tape
Set Height 500
Source demo_setup.tape

Hide 
Type " flyline set-cursor "
Show

Type "--interpolate-easing "
Sleep 400ms
Tab
Sleep 2500ms
Type "out"
Sleep 1500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
